data.title: 24 Puffer Dr, Whitney Pt, NY 13862
data.meta_description: Zillow has 44 photos of this $335,000 3 beds, 3 baths, 2,085 Square Feet single family home located at 24 Puffer Dr, Whitney Pt, NY 13862 built in 1965. MLS #325808.
data.text: Immaculate split level, completely updated and ready to welcome you home. The living room, kitchen and dining room make up a bright open area for sharing family time or entertaining! The large primary bedroom boasts a beautiful ensuite bath, and large closets. In the cooler months you can enjoy the warmth of not one, but two fireplaces. An enclosed porch in the back is the perfect place for morning coffee or enjoying the lush green of your acreage. There's two garages for your cars or toys, and an additional out back. The land boasts a beautiful pond, trails to hike or ride, and wooded land. The location is secluded enough to feel like country, but close enough to the highway to easily get to work, shopping or events. Qualified buyers may tour by appointment.
